<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	 "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
	  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>Welcome To NextThought</title>
		<style metal:use-macro="options/master/macros/style">
			#crimson-bar {
			background-color: #981b1e;
			width: 100%;
			height: 5px;
			margin-left: -30px;
			padding-right: 40px;
			}
			#logo-bar {
			margin-top: 20px;
			margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			body {
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-right: 0px;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
			a {
			text-decoration: none;
			color: #3fb3f6;
			}
			.tterm, strong {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #494949;
			}
			h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
			font-weight: bold;
			}
			h3{
				margin-bottom: 2px;
			}
			.point{margin-top: 0px;}

			.logo-bar.nti{margin-bottom: 0px}

			.logo-bar.nti{margin-bottom: 3px}

			.footer{margin-top: 0px}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="crimson-bar"></div>
		<div id="logo-bar">
			<img src="http://d2ixlfeu83tci.cloudfront.net/images/email_ou_logo.png" width="540" height="94"
			alt="The University of Oklahoma Logo." />
		</div>
		</div>
		<p>Hi <span tal:content="options/profile/realname" class="realname tterm">John Doe</span>!</p>

		<p>
			Welcome to the OU Digital Course Platform powered by
			NextThought!
		</p>
		<p>
			<strong>Username:</strong> <span tal:content="options/user/username" class="tterm-color">username</span> <br />
			<strong>Log in at:</strong> <a href="https://platform.ou.edu"
							tal:attributes="href request/application_url"
							tal:content="request/application_url">https://platform.ou.edu</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			Get the most out of your courses with this
			new social learning program and connect in ways
			never-before possible outside the classroom. Here are a
			few tips to get you started.
		</p>

		<h3><strong>Announcements</strong></h3>
		<p class="point">
			Keep an eye on the course dashboard for announcements about the platform or notes from faculty.
		</p>
		<h3><strong>Choose What You Share</strong></h3>
		<p class="point">
			When adding notes within a course, you can choose to share them with your classmates, a friend, or even keep them private.
		</p>
		<h3><strong>Friends</strong></h3>
		<p class="point">
			Your experience within the platform is as engaging as you make it. Add friends, create groups, and share notes.
		</p>

		<p>
		<a href="https://platform.ou.edu"
							tal:attributes="href request/application_url">Get
		started today.</a>
		</p>

		<br/>
			<div id="logo-bar nti">
			<img src="http://d2ixlfeu83tci.cloudfront.net/images/email_logo.png" width="177" height="25"
			alt="NextThought Logo" />
		</div>

		<p class="footer" style="font-size: smaller">
			If you feel this email was sent in error, or this account was created
			without your consent, you may email
			<a href="mailto:support@nextthought.com">support@nextthought.com</a>.
		</p>



	</body>
</html>
